headlines.description: — Jaylen Brown scored 30 points, Jayson Tatum had 21 and the Boston Celtics routed the Chicago Bulls 124-97 on Tuesday night to advance to the quarterfinals of the NBA In-Season Tournament.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jaylen Brown scores 30 points as Celtics pound Bulls 124-97 and advance in the In-Season Tournament

headlines.description: — Spencer Dinwiddie scored 23 points to lead the Brooklyn Nets to a 115-103 win over the Toronto Raptors on Tuesday night to win their third straight, but were knocked out of the NBA In-Season Tournament.
headlines.shortLinkText: Despite 115-103 win over Raptors, Nets knocked out of NBA In-Season Tournament

headlines.description: — Donovan Mitchell and the Cavaliers did everything in their power to stay in the NBA In-Season Tournament.
headlines.shortLinkText: Mitchell scores 40 as Cavaliers beat Hawks 128-105, but don't advance in NBA In-Season Tournament

headlines.description: — With the game on the line, the Milwaukee Bucks were just about perfect.
headlines.shortLinkText: Antetokounmpo, Lillard combine for 65, and Bucks earn quarterfinal berth by topping Heat 131-124

events.name: Charlotte Hornets at New York Knicks

headlines.description: — The New York Knicks were already making plans for a trip to Las Vegas after learning they had advanced to the quarterfinals of the NBA In-Season Tournament.
headlines.shortLinkText: Knicks rout Hornets, earn wild-card spot in East to advance in the In-Season Tournament

events.name: Oklahoma City Thunder at Minnesota Timberwolves

headlines.description: — Rudy Gobert had 17 points, 16 rebounds and four blocks, reserve Troy Brown Jr. scored a season-high 17 points and the Minnesota Timberwolves withstood an <a...
headlines.shortLinkText: Timberwolves top Thunder 106-103 despite Edwards injury with big all-around game by Gobert

headlines.description: — Luka Doncic had 41 points, nine rebounds and nine assists, and the Dallas Mavericks prevented the Houston Rockets from advancing to the quarterfinals of the NBA In-Season Tournament with a 121-115 victory on Tuesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Doncic scores 41, Mavericks prevent Rockets from advancing with a 121-115 victory

events.name: Golden State Warriors at Sacramento Kings

headlines.description: — Erasing most of a 24-point deficit assured the Sacramento Kings of advancing in the In-Season Tournament. Malik Monk made sure they did it with a win.
headlines.shortLinkText: Monk's late basket leads the Kings past the Warriors 124-123 to win In-Season Tournament group
